touch

To crate a file, the user can use touch in any place if there is permission for that.

  calvin@localhost:~/Documents/secret$ touch mySecretNote.txt
this command will create your folder 

If the user put spaces like;

  calvin@localhost:~/Documents/secret$ touch my Secret Note.txt
the program will creat 3 files, so we have to be careful about it! 


Not : touch is not using for creating folders!

